<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Start with the this one 1. The Warlord Wants Forever, It sets up most of the events for the series<br/>2. A Hunger Like no other<br/>3.No Rest for The Wicked<br/>4. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Start with the this one 1. The Warlord Wants Forever, It sets up most of the events for the series<br />2. A Hunger Like no other<br />3.No Rest for The Wicked<br />4. Wicked Deed on a Winters Night<br />5. Dark Needs at Nights Edge<br />6.Dark Desires after Dusk<br />7. Kiss of a Demon King<br />8. Deep Kiss of Winter<br />9. Pleasure of a Dark Princes<br />10. Demon From the Dark <br />11. Dreams of a Dark Warrior<br />12.Lothaire <br />13. Shadows Claim<br />14. MacRieve<br />15. Dark Skye<br />16. Sweet Ruin<br />17. Shadows Seduction <br />18.Wicked Abyss<br /><br />This is all that is currently out as far as I'm aware and I am on number 10 so far and HIGHLY RECOMMEND if paranormal romance is your thing. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
