<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/450744-is-it-necessary-to-read-this-novella">is it necessary to read this novella before diving into the series?? does it contribute to the world building seriously? because some of the reviews that i have read lead me to believe that the whole heroine capturing thing may be off putting?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_450744'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6388558-the-warlord-wants-forever">like</a></span>

