  <span id="freeText13654636336380776285" style="display:none">Another comfort reread.<br />Favourite book, favourite series, favourite universe.<br /><br />----------------------------------------<br />----------------------------------------<br /><br />First read:<br /><br />My dearest Immortals, I know I am about 10 years late BUT I think it is about time to get acquainted with each other...<br /><br /><i>
