              <span id="reviewTextContainer2754739252" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17021780941298797034"><b>3.5 STARS</b><br/><br/>I can&apos;t believe I&apos;m going to say this but . . . I think this one was TOO trashy for me. (Shocking, I know!)<br/><br/>Well, too trashy for me to consider it more than a smut read, hence the 3 stars.<br/><br/>But of course it was just a novella that introduces the IAD world. I have it on good authority that this series gets better and better, so I&apos;m in for the long haul. <br/><br/>Plus, <b>I LOVED the Valkyrie!</b> Myst and her sisters were highly entertaining with their unique brand of sarcastic bad-assery. Gotta love stron</span>
  <span id="freeText17021780941298797034" style="display:none"><b>3.5 STARS</b><br /><br />I can't believe I'm going to say this but . . . I think this one was TOO trashy for me. (Shocking, I know!)<br /><br />Well, too trashy for me to consider it more than a smut read, hence the 3 stars.<br /><br />But of course it was just a novella that introduces the IAD world. I have it on good authority that this series gets better and better, so I'm in for the long haul. <br /><br />Plus, <b>I LOVED the Valkyrie!</b> Myst and her sisters were highly entertaining with their unique brand of sarcastic bad-assery. Gotta love strong heroines who don't put up with bullshit.<br /><br />Looking forward to book 2!</span>
